data.description: SELLER OFFERING $10,000 TOWARD RATE BUY DOWN!!  Over 2,200 sq ft, concrete block, 3/2 + 2 Den home (Can easily be a 5/2) a 5 minute walk to the beach in the highly sought after Ocean Dunes. 3rd floor separate master suite with extensive natural lighting. Oversized living, family, and dining room. Beach Street Shoppes and restaurants, Tortugas Baseball Stadium and Brown & Brown HQ less than a 5 minute drive.  This is an investors dream or can easily be a perfect family home.
